query_light
Discworld object help
query_light

Name
.SI 5
query_light - Light level total of the object.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int query_light();
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This returns the total light level of the object.  Includeing any objects
that happen to be inside the current object.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
set_light, light, query_my_light, query_int_light
.EP
